name: AdsGod
overview:
AdsGod is an online pay per click ad-market. Publicise your ads to a large community using AdsGod advertiser account. Advertise using text and banner ads targeted to niche audience with full control on click rates and budget. Presenting a cost effective advertising system wherein you need to pay only for legitimate clicks on your ads.

AdsGod publisher account for webmasters. Monetize your website or blogs using AdsGod publisher account. Create stylish and modern ad display units matching your website or blog design. Display ads related to contents of your website or blog and earn from legitimate clicks send from your site.
